    { "@type": "Question", name: "How many boxes do I need to move a 3-bedroom house in Selangor?", acceptedAnswer: { "@type": "Answer", text: "A typical 3-bedroom terrace or apartment in Selangor requires 40–60 medium boxes plus 10–15 large boxes for books, clothes, and kitchen items. Add 5–10 small boxes for fragile collectibles and electronics accessories. It is always better to have 20% more boxes than you estimate needing." } },
